<p>
<a href="http://www.breconbeacons.org/horse-riding-pony-trekking" target="_blank">Horse-riding</a><br/>There are a number of equestrian routes with spectacular scenery and a wealth of wildlife in Fforest Fawr.</p></li>
<li>
<p>
<a href="http://www.breconbeacons.org/caving-potholing" target="_blank">Caving</a><br/>Caves such as Ogof Ffynnon DduÂ and Porth yr Ogof are famed for their impressive mouths and lengthy, complex tunnel systems.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Wildlife Watching
